t"},"\n        ",["ARTICLE",{"class":"col-xs-12 service full clearfix"},"\n\n    \n        \n\n    \n    ",["DIV",{"class":"content"},"\n      \n            ",["DIV",{"class":"field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field--item"},["H2",{"id":"check"},"Check your bin day and sign up for reminders"],["P",{},"You can use the following link to:"],["UL",{},["LI",{},"check your bin day to view your next four weeks of collections by typing your street or postcode"],["LI",{},"sign up for reminders to stay up to date with your collections"]],["P",{},"You won’t need to create an account to do this."],["P",{"class":"btn btn-lg btn-success"},["A",{"href":"https://myaccount.wrexham.gov.uk/en/AchieveForms/?form_uri=sandbox-publish://AF-Process-ceb55423-9f5d-4124-b713-805ac7a73e3e/AF-Stage-854336b9-1221-4e6a-88d7-785fb2f8e340/definition.json&redirectlink=%2Fen&cancelRedirectLink=%2Fen&consentMessage=yes"},"Start now"]],["P",{},"If you sign up for reminders you’ll receive a weekly email the day before each collection - so you never have to remember what bin goes out when."],["P",{},"The reminders will also reflect any planned changes to the collection schedule."]],"\n      \n      ",["DIV",{"class":"field field--name-field-content field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field--items"},"\n              ",["DIV",{"class":"field--item"},"  ",["DIV",{"class":"paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default"},"\n          \n            ",["DIV",{"class":"field field--name-field-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field--item"},["H2",{},"How often are collections?"],["P",{},"We collect household waste on alternate weeks. Recycling containers and food waste are collected on a weekly basis – on the same day as your bin collection."],["P",{},"Your black or blue wheelie bin is collected one week and, if you are signed up to the garden waste collection service, your green wheelie bin is collected the following week (apart from during December to February, when green bins are emptied monthly)."],["H2",{},"What time should I put my bin out?"],["P",{},"Make sure your bin and recycling container is put out by 7.30am on your collection day."]],"\n      \n      "],"\n"],"\n              ",["DIV",{"class":"field--item"},"  ",["DIV",{"class":"paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default"},"\n          \n            ",["DIV",{"class":"field field--name-field-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field--item"},["H2",{},"Severe weather"],["P",{},"During periods of severe weather, such as snow, it is possible that collections will be disrupted or even suspended. For the latest information please check out the ",["A",{"href":"https://news.wrexham.gov.uk/"},"Council News blog"],", ",["A",{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/wrexhamcouncil"},"Facebook (external link)"]," or ",["A",{"href":"https://twitter.com/wrexhamcbc"},"X (formerly Twitter) (external link)"],"."],["H2",{},"Bank holidays"],["H3",{},"Easter, May, August, Christmas and New Year"],["P",{},"Collection days will change during this period. "],["P",{},"You can ",["A",{"href":"https://www.wrexham.gov.uk/service/when-are-my-bins-collected#check"},"follow the link at the top of this page to check your bin day and sign up for reminders"]," which will tell you about any changes."]],"\n      \n      "],"\n"],"\n          "],"\n  \n    "],"\n\n  "],"\n\n\n  "],"\n\n              "],"\n\n                "],"\n  "],"\n\n\n    ",["DIV",{"class":"footer-container"},"\n    ",["FOOTER",{"class":"footer container"},"\n        ",["DIV",{"class":"region region-footer"},"\n    ",["SECTION",{"class":"az-list-letters block block-firmstep-az block-firmstep-a-z-nav-block clearfix","id":"block-firmstepaznavigation","aria-label":"Firmstep A-Z Navigation"},"\n  \n    \n\n      ",["UL",{"class":"item-list__az_list"},["LI",{},["A",{"href":"https://www.wrexham.gov.uk/a-z/a"},"A"]],["LI",{},["A",{"href":"https://www.wre